.SH PARAMETERS
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBcollection\fP: A \fBmongoc_collection_t\fP\&.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBnew_db\fP: The name of the new database.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBnew_name\fP: The new name for the collection.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBdrop_target_before_rename\fP: If an existing collection matches the new name, drop it before the rename.
